      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我加上allows这条线。另外，PaymentGateway还需要对下游模块施加一些约束条件吧？比如安全策略。",
